00:19:25,208 --> 00:19:27,583
Looks like we've got
a real match on our hands.

258
00:19:27,666 --> 00:19:30,583
[RUI] I bet Hachisu wins, cause
she's the toughest girl I know!

259
00:19:30,666 --> 00:19:31,583
[SHIKIBU]
C'mon!

260
00:19:31,666 --> 00:19:33,250
[gasps]
Shikibu, wait!

261
00:19:33,333 --> 00:19:34,833
[SAIZOU grunts]

262
00:19:34,916 --> 00:19:36,791
[HACHISU] Saizou,
what do you think you're doing?

263
00:19:36,875 --> 00:19:38,375
[SAIZOU]
I'm helping.

264
00:19:38,458 --> 00:19:39,791
[SHICHIGEN]
I don't need any help from you.

265
00:19:39,875 --> 00:19:41,708
I'm a samurai, remember?

266
00:19:41,791 --> 00:19:44,583
[SAIZOU] Fine. Then I'm
on Hachisu's side.

267
00:19:44,666 --> 00:19:46,583
[WOMAN B]
Food's ready, everyone!

268
00:19:46,666 --> 00:19:47,833
Come and get it!

269
00:19:47,916 --> 00:19:49,625
[CHILDREN cheering]

270
00:19:49,708 --> 00:19:51,166
[WOMAN B]
Hibiki, stay.

271
00:19:51,250 --> 00:19:54,041
We'll come get you once the kids
have all been taken care of.

272
00:19:54,125 --> 00:19:56,791
Sure. The weather's
so nice today,

273
00:19:56,875 --> 00:19:59,500
I don't mind staying out
a little while longer.

274
00:20:03,375 --> 00:20:04,500
[JOUJIN]
Well, well.

275
00:20:04,583 --> 00:20:05,750
[HIBIKI gasps]

276
00:20:05,833 --> 00:20:08,041
[JOUJIN] You cannot see,
and Hachirou isn't here

277
00:20:08,125 --> 00:20:09,875
to watch over you.

278
00:20:09,958 --> 00:20:11,208
Joujin?

279
00:20:14,041 --> 00:20:17,750
No. Joujin died long ago.

280
00:20:17,833 --> 00:20:20,333
How can you be so certain?

281
00:20:20,416 --> 00:20:23,791
In truth, I did perish
when last we met.

282
00:20:23,875 --> 00:20:25,250
But then...

283
00:20:25,333 --> 00:20:27,041
Tenzen.

284
00:20:27,125 --> 00:20:30,208
[JOUJIN] I'd expect no less
from the leader of the Iga.

285
00:20:30,291 --> 00:20:31,791
[HIBIKI whimpers]

286
00:20:31,875 --> 00:20:34,458
[JOUJIN] Nobunaga- <i>sama</i> 's
soul has returned to Hell.

287
00:20:34,541 --> 00:20:36,291
Hachirou is gone.

288
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:40,500
Since you rendered
your eyes completely useless.

289
00:20:40,583 --> 00:20:43,458
I can no longer
harness the Ouka.

290
00:20:43,541 --> 00:20:46,166
However, there
is one course of action

291
00:20:46,250 --> 00:20:47,416
still available.

292
00:20:47,500 --> 00:20:48,708
[HIBIKI whimpers]

293
00:20:48,791 --> 00:20:49,958
[JOUJIN]
That's right.

294
00:20:50,041 --> 00:20:53,041
I shall fill your womb
with the seed of life.

295
00:20:53,125 --> 00:20:57,916
And you will be with child,
and bear forth my heir.

296
00:20:58,000 --> 00:21:00,166
No one will come to save you.

297
00:21:00,250 --> 00:21:03,250
Give up, and submit
yourself to my will!

298
00:21:03,333 --> 00:21:04,708
[HIBIKI grunts]

299
00:21:08,083 --> 00:21:10,000
Your blood is strong.

300
00:21:10,083 --> 00:21:13,875
If my essence were to
combine with your bloodline.

301
00:21:13,958 --> 00:21:18,625
We would create a technique
that would surpass Ouka.

302
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:22,083
[JOUJIN]
With our two bloodlines mixed,

303
00:21:22,166 --> 00:21:25,916
we shall truly make
this world a living Hell!

304
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:27,541
[gasps]

305
00:21:31,916 --> 00:21:37,166
[yells]

306
00:21:37,250 --> 00:21:40,000
[TENZEN screeches]

307
00:21:53,625 --> 00:21:55,291
Hachirou...

308
00:22:16,708 --> 00:22:19,958
[HADAEBOU sighs]
Bright, with a healthy breeze.

309
00:22:20,041 --> 00:22:22,416
Couldn't ask for a
finer day to travel.

